text: Yankton is a city in and the county seat of Yankton County, in the southern part of the U.S. state of South Dakota. It became a city in 1889, and 15,411 people lived there at the 2020 census. Yankton is located near the Missouri River. == References == == Other websites == *City of Yankton website Category:County seats in South Dakota Category:Cities in South Dakota Category:1889 establishments in South Dakota
